<p style="background:white"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">It pleases us to invite you to the 15<sup>th</sup> Edition <b>of IIM Bangalore’s Annual Business Fest: Vista</b>! It has been a long journey since Vista’s humble roots and Vista has only been growing from strength to strength. Over the years, Vista has attracted the Who’s-Who from the world of business, politics and Entertainment, including <b>Mr. Subramanian Swamy, Mr. Kamal Hassan, Mr. Ronnie Screwvala, Mr. Narain Karthikeyan</b> and many more. This year too, Vista brings to you a power packed line-up of speakers, including <b>Mr. Mani Shankar Aiyar, Mr. Siddhartha Roy Kapur and Mr. Rajdeep Sardesai</b>. Vista grown over the years to now attract students from across <b>350+ campuses</b>. With a line-up of more than <b>40+ events and 15 lakh</b> in Prize money, Vista attracts the greatest minds of from across the country. It is the coliseum for the future managers of this country; a place where they pit themselves against the best in the business. </span></p>
